HEADWORD: Heavy spar
<hw>Heav"y spar`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>Native barium
sulphate or barite, -- so called because of its high specific gravity as
compared with other non-metallic minerals.</def>⟦br⟧
